      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional & Technical Fit: Unified lakehouse platform with full T-SQL compatibility\n\nScalability & Performance: Petabyte-scale processing with auto-scaling compute\n\nEase of Integration & Use: 200+ connectors, low-code to pro-code flexibility\n\nSecurity & Governance: Enterprise-grade compliance with FSI certifications\n\nVendor Experience & References: 30+ years in data platforms, deep FSI expertise\n\nTotal Cost of Ownership: Capacity-based pricing, proven ROI",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional & Technical Fit: Unified lakehouse platform with full T-SQL compatibility\n\nScalability & Performance: Petabyte-scale processing with auto-scaling compute\n\nEase of Integration & Use: 200+ connectors, low-code to pro-code flexibility\n\nSecurity & Governance: Enterprise-grade compliance with FSI certifications\n\nVendor Experience & References: 30+ years in data platforms, deep FSI expertise\n\nTotal Cost of Ownership: Capacity-based pricing, proven ROI",
